    <p>Dream provides an AI-driven sales tool accessible via subscription. The Service is available through online sign-up, including options for registration through Google accounts.</p>

    <h2>2. Account Registration</h2>
    <p>To access certain features of the Service, you must create an account. When creating an account, you agree to provide accurate and complete information. Users are prohibited from creating multiple accounts for the purpose of obtaining free credits or circumventing the terms of this agreement.</p>
    <p>We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that we believe are created for the purpose of abuse, including but not limited to, obtaining multiple free credits, harassment, or any illegal activities.</p>

    <h2>3. Subscription and Payments</h2>
    <p>Access to the Service is provided on a subscription basis. The terms of payment, billing cycles, and applicable taxes are defined in the contract you sign upon subscription. If you wish to cancel your subscription, cancellation policies will be governed by the terms of the contract you agreed to at the time of subscription.</p>

    <h2>4. User Conduct</h2>
    <p>By using the Service, you agree not to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Use the Service for any unlawful purposes or to violate any laws.</li>
        <li>Harass, abuse, or harm others through the Service.</li>
        <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems or those of other users.</li>
        <li>Create multiple accounts to exploit free credits or any promotional offers.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Termination</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right to terminate or suspend your access to the Service at any time, with or without notice, for conduct that we believe violates these Terms, is harmful to other users, or is illegal.</p>

    <h2>6. Governing Law</h2>
    <p>These Terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the United Kingdom. Any disputes arising out of or in connection with these Terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of the United Kingdom.</p>

    <h2>7. Changes to the Terms</h2>
    <p>We may update these Terms from time to time. If we make material changes, we will notify you by email or through the Service before the changes take effect. Your continued use of the Service after the updated Terms are in effect will constitute your acceptance of the changes.</p>

    <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about these Terms, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@usedream.ai">privacy@usedream.ai</a>.</p>

    <h2>9. Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>Please review our <a href="https://usedream.ai/privacy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a> to understand our practices regarding the collection and use of your personal information.</p>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

